full_text: I also strongly prefer romantic and non-sexual content as whole, but given how society is it's harder to find content that isn't at least marginally sexual. Being an adult woman means if I want to watch content aimed at my age group it's usually sexualized in one way or another.

full_text: There is a certain layer of separation with drawn and written fiction that make me feel comfortable enough I can consume it safely. Live action stuff makes me feel super repulsed and grossed out because there's less separation and I start to feel extremely put off.
